# Behavioural eval run artifacts — heavy and fully regenerable by re-running
# the runner scripts. We version the harness + the human-readable results
# (reports, grading.json, trigger-results*.json), NOT the raw run dumps.

# Full model transcripts (~0.3–0.9 MB each)
**/transcript.jsonl

# Per-run state copied out of the scratch repo (.state, spec.md, plan.md, …)
**/agentic-loop-state/
**/outputs/

# Misc per-run scratch
**/runner-timing.json
**/hook-block-detected.txt

# Static HTML viewer (regenerable from the JSON)
*.html

# (*.log is already ignored by the repo-root .gitignore — stderr.log,
#  branch-commits.log, src-files.log, trigger-*.log, viewer.log, etc.)
